description:
{ overall : 4 stars }

{ food : 4 stars }
* Pecos Poached Eggs - 3.5 stars, needed more flavor
* Queso And Chips, Chorizo, Scallions - 4 stars, although it didn't taste like queso cheese it had good flavor.  it actually tastes (and has consistency) of the seven-11 nacho cheese.  i should know, eating it almost every other week in middle school!
* Coffee-rubbed Brisket Sandwich - 4.5 stars, this was a winner winner chicken dinner.  so much flavor and bread reminded me of a lobster roll. yummy butter goodness

{ drinks : 4.5 stars }
* margaritas - yum!

{ service : 4 stars }
* friendly and attentive staff

{ prices : 4.5 stars }
* so reasonable!

definitely want to try dinner!
